title: "Which Moats Survive When AI Makes Software Cheap?"
date: "2026-04-28"
description: "AI makes software cheaper to reproduce. Durable advantages still require elapsed time, compound through use, and protect something the market will continue to value."
tags: ["ai", "moats", "strategy", "defensibility"]
